<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><entry xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="entry_ænkʼaryn" xml:lang="os"><form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>ænkʼaryn</orth><form type="inflected" subtype="ptcp"><orth>ænkʼard</orth></form></form><form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>ænkʼarun</orth><form type="inflected" subtype="ptcp"><orth>ænkʼard</orth></form></form><sense><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>чувствовать</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>to feel</q></cit></sense><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>воспринимать</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>to perceive</q></cit></sense></sense><re><form type="lemma"><orth>xīmæ ænkʼaryn</orth></form><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>принимать %bза%b свой счет</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>to take smth. personally</q></cit></sense></re><cit type="exampleGroup" corresp="#sense_ænkʼaryn." n=""><cit type="example"><quote>mijjag æ zærdæmæ esti ku bankʼara</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>как бы он чего-нибудь не принял близко к сердцу</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>what if he took something to heart</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_MD"/><biblScope>1937 I 29</biblScope></bibl></cit><cit type="example"><quote>ūcy wajʒæf æz mæxīmæ ænkʼаrуn</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>этот упрек я принимаю за свой счет</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>I take this blame personally</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Сл."/></bibl></cit></cit><cit type="exampleGroup" corresp="#sense_." n=""><cit type="example"><quote>mijjag æ zærdæmæ esti ku bankʼara</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>как бы он чего-нибудь не принял близко к сердцу</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>what if he took something to heart</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_MD"/><biblScope>1937 I 29</biblScope></bibl></cit><cit type="example"><quote>ūcy wajʒæf æz mæxīmæ ænkʼаrуn</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>этот упрек я принимаю за свой счет</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>I take this blame personally</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Сл."/></bibl></cit></cit><etym xml:lang="ru">Восходит <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>*han-kār-</w></mentioned>, ср. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/><w>angārdan</w></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w>angarīdan: angār-</w><gloss><q>размышлять</q></gloss></mentioned>, , ‘предполагать’, ‘думать’, <mentioned xml:lang="pal"><lang/><w>hangārtan</w><gloss><q>помнить</q></gloss></mentioned>, ‘иметь в виду’, ‘принимать в расчет’, ср. <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/><w>%r2%rkar-</w><gloss><q>помнить</q></gloss></mentioned>, ‘воспринимать’ (<bibl corresp="#ref_AiW"><biblScope>449</biblScope></bibl>). Неожиданное появление смычно-гортанного %ikʼ%i наводит на мысль, не имела ли места контаминация с каким-нибудь иноязычным словом. Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="mn"><lang/><w>anqar-</w><gloss><q>воспринимать</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">It traces back to <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>*han-kār-</w></mentioned>, ср. <mentioned xml:lang=""><lang/><w>angārdan</w></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang=""><w>angarīdan: angār-</w><gloss><q>to reflect</q></gloss></mentioned>, , ‘to suppose’, ‘to think’, <mentioned xml:lang="pal"><lang/><w>hangārtan</w><gloss><q>to remember</q></gloss></mentioned>, ‘to mean’, ‘to take into consideration’, compare <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/><w>%r2%rkar-</w><gloss><q>to remember</q></gloss></mentioned>, ‘to perceive’ (<bibl corresp="#ref_AiW"><biblScope>449</biblScope></bibl>). Unexpected appearance of ejective consonant %ikʼ%i suggests the assumption of the contamination with some foreign word. Compare <mentioned xml:lang="mn"><lang/><w>anqar-</w><gloss><q>to perceive</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym></entry>